  "text": "We can fix this gauge invariance by taking generalized a-gauges and construct the corresponding gauge fixed action S n,{α} by the procedure parallel to the case of open string field theory as we discussed in ref. [CITATION_1] . Here we only present the resulting gauge fixed action as follows. It is given by the sum of the gauge invariant action S min n and the (anti-)ghosts plus gauge fixing terms:",
